“What changed? Why hasn’t he[Reinhart] recused himself on this case? Obama must be very proud of him right now!” Trump said, referring to his predecessor, former President Barack Obama.

Trump later wrote on Truth Social, “WITCH HUNT!!!”

Trump’s two eldest sons were among many who ridiculed the hefty redactions, sharing images of many of the completely blacked-out pages.

“Well this really clears things up,” Donald Trump Jr., 44, tweeted alongside an image of three such unreadable pages. 

“They tell you with a straight face that they want ‘transparency’ knowing that their media lackeys will run with it as though it’s a fact. Then they release this. Transparency my ass!!!” he tweeted.

Eric Trump, 38, posted an image of one such page — writing sarcastically, “Transparency.”..
